content: For Freedivers
What an amazing app to use.So user friendly with awesome results
All the flexibility you need creating standard O2 and CO2 tables without being complicated. I love it.

I've tried a couple other apnea training apps, including ones with more bells and whistles, but this one is my favorite so far - easy to navigate and modify, but still gives me what I need. Beginners should be aware that the default settings are not intended as a starting point in your training. Do some research and/or get some professional training to determine your starting level and modify accordingly.
replyContent: Thank you for your comment! The predefined tables are removed from the initial install, instead the app offers to users to generate tables that match their current level (based on the PB).
